{"tid":1978736,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三招學識揀口罩　教你公司查冊　讀懂CE、FDA認證","createTime":"2020-04-19T02:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T02:48:51.000Z","uid":157795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac4abfb6ba8fc61b0b171b83dc1ff5a1fe79ee3","tid":1978736,"uid":157795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/462428/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E4%B8%89%E6%8B%9B%E5%AD%B8%E8%AD%98%E6%8F%80%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-01%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%9F%A5%E5%86%8A-%E8%AE%80%E6%87%82ce-fda%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%259F%25A5%2F462428%2F%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-01%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2586%258A-%25E8%25AE%2580%25E6%2587%2582ce-fda%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2589&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDhQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=e75f112a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/462428/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E4%B8%89%E6%8B%9B%E5%AD%B8%E8%AD%98%E6%8F%80%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-01%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%9F%A5%E5%86%8A-%E8%AE%80%E6%87%82ce-fda%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89</a><br />\n<br />\n招式1：核對廠商及經銷商名稱及地址<br />\n內地公司查冊：<a href=\"http://www.tianyancha.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tianyancha.com&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDhQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=b7f382b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.tianyancha.com</a><br />\n其他國家公司查冊：<a href=\"http://www.opencorporates.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.opencorporates.com&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDhQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=d2d9b49e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.opencorporates.com</a> <br />\n<br />\n招式2：細看CE認證規格、資料及標籤是否齊全<br />\n質檢顧問黃喜龍指出，CE認證口罩的包裝盒必須印有以下三批資料：製造商、歐盟代表公司及歐盟進口商名稱及地址；出廠日期、有效日期、產品批號、產品序列號，及產品說明；有特定標記及要求。然而，記者早前抽查的40盒口罩中，17盒包裝盒均印有歐盟CE認證商標，但不少都沒有達到CE包裝盒要求。<br />\n<br />\n黃續表示，現時口罩要入口歐盟國家，必須獲得歐盟CE認證。但獲CE認證，不等於一定獲印發證書，主要視乎口罩的報關用途，例如未經滅菌的醫用口罩，廠商只須作自我聲明，以及準備相關的醫療管理系統、測試及技術文檔，以供將來歐盟海關或主管當局進行抽查；若屬已滅菌的醫用口罩，廠商便須交由歐盟指定的公告機構進行CE認證審核（Compliance Audit），之後便會獲印發證書。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4346595/org/821371ecc21eb0dae16d72ba99021da1.jpg/TSmQn5MKaNg3FneKpsamPpE41xdATxdf7aTn7u2k5-4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4346595%2Forg%2F821371ecc21eb0dae16d72ba99021da1.jpg%2FTSmQn5MKaNg3FneKpsamPpE41xdATxdf7aTn7u2k5-4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3fd405e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，有CE證書的口罩均有一個認證代碼，它會印在盒上CE標記旁邊，公眾可到歐盟網上資料庫（NANDO）查閱代碼，以辨真偽。獲CE認證但無證書的口罩則沒有認證代碼。<br />\n招式3：FDA無證書、上歐盟網址查核可疑證書樣本<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4344777/org/a10e9579bdc1eac0baff7b92fa9b0b21.jpg/9jO6R3mfn1yBnTR4kjkzBVdOwmAycdg54vQLRuL0C0Y?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4344777%2Forg%2Fa10e9579bdc1eac0baff7b92fa9b0b21.jpg%2F9jO6R3mfn1yBnTR4kjkzBVdOwmAycdg54vQLRuL0C0Y%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b35b3787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除歐盟的CE認證外，美國FDA認證也廣為人知。FDA認證是由美國藥物及食物管理局進行審查、批核及註冊。但黃喜龍提醒，FDA認證是不會為產品發放證書，坊間流傳的FDA證書都與口罩質素無關，如果有廠商或商戶出示有關證書，力銷該批口罩，市民需要留意。網上亦有專門研究口罩的群組成員戲稱，買口罩要如果發現FDA「證書」，均與品質無關，不必理會。<br />\n<br />\n此外，因應市面上出現大量偽造的「歐盟認證」口罩證書，歐盟屬下的歐洲安全聯盟在其網頁上列出數十款可疑證書樣本，市民可於此頁查核證書外貌是否類同。"},{"pid":"6eb5d5190b2476848fff9f03fb4b449d25d026e2","tid":1978736,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"出呢啲文但係唔提CE (支那Export)扮CE(歐盟)，支那01真係..."}]}